1
00:01:54,660 --> 00:01:57,810
明 嘉靖年间
During the reign of Ming Emperor Jiajing (1522-1567)

2
00:01:57,830 --> 00:02:03,720
由于朝廷海禁地方官府腐败沿海倭寇蜂起
Japanese pirates raided the coastlines of China because of the sea ban.

3
00:02:03,750 --> 00:02:07,060
其中被认为乃倭寇之首的
The chief of these Japanese pirates

4
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:11,610
却是一个安徽人王直屡次进犯沿海
was actually a Han Chinese man called Wang Zhi.

5
00:02:12,910 --> 00:02:14,520
嘉靖三十六年
In 1557,

6
00:02:14,620 --> 00:02:17,930
浙江总督胡宗宪说服王直投诚
The Zhejiang commander led Wang

7
00:02:17,950 --> 00:02:19,930
助除倭寇之患
to turn against the pirates.

8
00:02:20,290 --> 00:02:24,940
怎料王直随即被杭州竭巡按王本固收押
But Wang was subsequently imprisoned by the Governor of Hangzhou.

9
00:02:24,950 --> 00:02:29,270
倭寇不降反四处生事攻击浙江沿海
So the pirates continued to raid the coastal areas of Zhejiang.

10
00:02:29,870 --> 00:02:33,560
此时王直之义子毛海峰
Wang's godson Mao Haifeng

11
00:02:33,580 --> 00:02:35,850
与一支上千人的倭寇部队
and over 1,000 pirates

12
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:38,060
占据了浙江岑港
occupied Cengang

13
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:42,560
大量自沿海抢来的各种物资集结于此
with the loot pillaged from the coast.

14
00:02:43,250 --> 00:02:47,560
明军在俞大猷指挥下围攻了五个多月
The army under Commander Yu Dayou besieged them for 5 months.

15
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,900
浙江总兵  俞大猷
Yu Dayou Garrison Commander of Zhejiang"

16
00:02:58,777 --> 00:03:05,777
荡       寇       风       云

17
00:03:07,777 --> 00:03:11,111
毛     劲     松     封     装
Mao Jinsong encapsulation

18
00:04:15,450 --> 00:04:16,350
冲呀
Charge!

19
00:04:36,950 --> 00:04:38,930
一起 开炮
Fire!

20
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:55,970
冲呀
Charge!

21
00:05:33,370 --> 00:05:35,520
将军
General!

22
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,230
将军
General!

23
00:05:37,870 --> 00:05:39,690
将军 你没事吧
Are you alright?

24
00:05:40,370 --> 00:05:42,020
将军 快要顶不住了
We can't hold them off!

25
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:43,140
撤吧
We should fall back.

26
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:51,640
撤退
Retreat!

27
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:34,600
大人
Sir!

28
00:06:34,910 --> 00:06:37,270
他们就这样傻傻的
Like fools,

29
00:06:37,540 --> 00:06:40,140
每次按着同一时辰来攻我们呢
they launch their attacks at the same hour each time.

30
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:42,720
铁炮队 收队
Guns Unit dismissed!

31
00:06:45,290 --> 00:06:47,230
按时早饭
They eat on time,

32
00:06:47,620 --> 00:06:50,930
按时冲锋 按时败退
attack and retreat on time.

33
00:06:51,290 --> 00:06:54,390
明军真有纪律呀
The Ming troops have such discipline!

34
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:56,480
大人
Sir!

35
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:59,100
部队们见一直都是浪人在领功
The ronins get all the credit.

36
00:06:59,250 --> 00:07:01,680
士兵们不会觉得没趣吗
Won't the soldiers feel snubbed?

37
00:07:01,700 --> 00:07:02,430
谢谢
Thank you.

38
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,730
对付这些明军
The ronins are sufficient

39
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:09,230
浪人就够了
to take on the Ming troops.

40
00:07:10,370 --> 00:07:12,520
既然明军如此不济
If these troops are so pathetic,

41
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:15,270
将军为何不进攻内地
why didn't you invade the inland

42
00:07:15,750 --> 00:07:18,400
胁迫朝廷放我义父
and force the Ming Court to release my godfather?

43
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,190
将军
General,

44
00:07:23,750 --> 00:07:26,270
忘了松蒲大人的话了
have you forgotten what Lord Matsura said?

45
00:07:27,660 --> 00:07:28,890
海峰兄
Haifeng,

46
00:07:29,750 --> 00:07:31,190
不用提醒我
no need to remind me.

47
00:07:32,290 --> 00:07:39,810
五峰大人对松蒲藩的贡献 我们都很清楚
We're aware of Master Wufeng's (Wang Zhi) contribution to the Matsura clan.

48
00:07:40,540 --> 00:07:43,850
但 松蒲大人说过这里的所有行动
But Lord Matsura made it clear

49
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:45,980
不能以他的名义进行
we're not acting on his behalf.

50
00:07:46,450 --> 00:07:49,180
我们是倭寇 不是松蒲军
We're wokou.

51
00:07:49,330 --> 00:07:51,020
我们是贼
We are pirates,

52
00:07:52,830 --> 00:07:57,020
领头的是五峰大人
under the command of Master Wufeng.

53
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:03,730
当六十个浪人
If 60 ronins

54
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:06,230
可以直达南京城下捣乱明军时
can reach Nanjing and defeat the Ming troops,

55
00:08:06,660 --> 00:08:08,560
我们一千部队
we have a regiment of 1,000 men,

56
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:11,440
为何只守不攻
why can't we take the offensive?

57
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:16,560
孙子用兵之法
According to the Art of War,

58
00:08:17,620 --> 00:08:20,480
十则围之五则攻之
encircle when we outnumber the enemy 10 to 1

59
00:08:20,580 --> 00:08:23,430
明军以十倍于我军的军队围攻我
and attack when it's 5 to 1.

60
00:08:24,370 --> 00:08:26,480
我们可以守住
We only managed to hold them off

61
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:30,770
是倚仗地利天险
because we have the benefit of a natural barrier.

62
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:35,270
我一千军队一旦没有了地利
Without that edge,

63
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:38,480
也一样会输
we will lose just the same.

64
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:43,540
我们会像那60个浪人一样结束
We will end up like those 60 ronins.

65
00:08:43,540 --> 00:08:44,440
大人
Sir!

66
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:48,930
大人太高估明国的军队了
You have overestimated the Ming troops.

67
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:52,560
光是南方就有驻军二十万
They have 200,000 men stationed in the south

68
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:57,020
对手是明国将军俞大猷
under the command of Yu Dayou.

69
00:08:57,540 --> 00:09:02,850
明国的军队贪生怕死朝廷官员贪污腐败
Ming troops are cowards and Court officials are corrupted.

70
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:08,320
多来几个俞大猷又有什么用
A few more like Yu Dayou means nothing.

71
00:09:10,870 --> 00:09:12,350
最近呢
Recently,

72
00:09:13,540 --> 00:09:17,940
有一个文武双全叫戚继光的将军出现
a general named Qi Jiguang showed up

73
00:09:18,410 --> 00:09:21,190
他带领明军连战连胜
and led the Ming troops in winning several battles.

74
00:09:23,370 --> 00:09:24,900
戚继光
Qi Jiguang?

75
00:09:40,870 --> 00:09:41,940
在干什么
What are they doing?

76
00:09:42,830 --> 00:09:44,150
这班畜牲
Bastards!

77
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,730
由得他们吧
Leave them alone.

78
00:09:48,950 --> 00:09:50,020
为什么
Why?

79
00:09:51,290 --> 00:09:52,230
老师
Sensei

80
00:09:52,830 --> 00:09:57,060
我们是武士却要跟这些流氓一起作战
why should samurais fight alongside ronins

81
00:09:57,830 --> 00:09:59,520
还要看着他们胡作非为
and put up with their atrocious behavior?

82
00:10:02,540 --> 00:10:04,890
这只是各取所需
To each his own.

83
00:10:06,160 --> 00:10:08,940
我们漂洋过海来到这里
We came from across the ocean

84
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:11,440
是要为大名取得财富
to help the Daimyo build his fortune

85
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:14,940
购买火枪好让主公强大起来
and to buy firearms to make him powerful.

86
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:18,060
而他们要的是
They came here

87
00:10:19,290 --> 00:10:21,940
女人钱财
for women and money.

88
00:10:26,450 --> 00:10:29,980
他们的行径不合武士仁义
Their behavior is unworthy of a samurai.

89
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:33,770
但也得满足他们
But we must keep them happy

90
00:10:33,830 --> 00:10:36,100
这样他们才会卖命的
so they will risk their lives for us.

91
00:10:38,700 --> 00:10:41,860
少主 你只要记住
You must remember

92
00:10:42,950 --> 00:10:46,010
我们能在此赚钱买武器
we're here to make money and buy weapons

93
00:10:46,290 --> 00:10:49,060
只是为了统一天下
in order Japan can rule the world.

94
00:10:49,830 --> 00:10:52,150
其他的事情都不重要
Nothing else matters.

95
00:10:52,870 --> 00:10:55,480
要打败明国
To defeat the Ming Court,

96
00:10:57,410 --> 00:11:02,480
不能只谈仁义也要有战略
benevolence is not enough. We also need strategy.

97
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:05,980
待山川少主你成了大名之后
When you become the Daimyo, Master Yamagawa,

98
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:08,440
到时候再多谈仁义吧
you can be more benevolent.

99
00:11:08,870 --> 00:11:11,980
万一被明国知道是我们松蒲出兵
If the Ming Court found out we're from the Matsura Army,

100
00:11:13,540 --> 00:11:16,020
会让松蒲藩陷于危险
it will endanger the Matsura clan.

101
00:11:17,330 --> 00:11:20,150
我们是倭寇
We're pirates,

102
00:11:23,950 --> 00:11:27,060
穷凶极恶的倭寇
savage pirates.

103
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:31,270
少主你懂吗
Do you understand?

104
00:11:45,910 --> 00:11:47,060
俞将军
General Yu!

105
00:11:47,540 --> 00:11:48,390
胡大人
Commander Hu!

106
00:11:48,620 --> 00:11:49,440
你受伤了
You're injured!

107
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:51,390
小伤而已
It's nothing.

108
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:54,650
我正准备天黑之前再冲锋
I intend to launch another attack before dark.

109
00:11:54,660 --> 00:11:58,720
"Hu Zongxian Supreme Commander of Zhejiang"

110
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:02,440
像这样的冲锋有用吗
What's the use?

111
00:12:04,500 --> 00:12:05,600
俞将军
General Yu!

112
00:12:06,040 --> 00:12:08,140
宁绍台参将戚继光
I'm Assistant Regional Military Commissioner Qi Jiguang.

113
00:12:09,700 --> 00:12:11,060
你就是戚继光
So you're Qi Jiguang.

114
00:12:12,250 --> 00:12:13,650
你说我冲锋没用
If you think my plan doesn't work,

115
00:12:13,910 --> 00:12:15,770
那你有什么有用的方法
you have a better idea?

116
00:12:15,910 --> 00:12:17,230
尚无方法
Not yet.

117
00:12:18,370 --> 00:12:21,310
不过像俞将军这样冲锋
You've been doing this

118
00:12:21,330 --> 00:12:23,230
也有好几个月了吧
for several months, right?

119
00:12:26,700 --> 00:12:27,850
俞将军
General Yu,

120
00:12:29,290 --> 00:12:31,560
京中再三催促
the Imperial Court is getting impatient.

121
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:35,020
离一月破敌之日只有二十天
You have 20 days left of your one-month deadline.

122
00:12:35,830 --> 00:12:37,060
所以呢
That's why

123
00:12:37,620 --> 00:12:40,730
我打算让元敬训练的新军试一试
I intend to let Jiguang give it a try with his New Army.

124
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:42,140
元敬的新军
They have wiped out pirates

125
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:45,270
已经接连在浙西剿灭了三路贼兵
in western Zhejiang in 3 successive battles.

126
00:12:49,830 --> 00:12:51,060
俞将军
General Yu,

127
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:55,180
你已经久攻了好几个月了吧
you have been fighting for months.

128
00:12:56,250 --> 00:12:57,900
人马疲乏
You must be exhausted.

129
00:12:58,290 --> 00:13:01,810
而且你的属下多以水师为主
Besides, most of your men are trained at sea...

130
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:04,690
属下遵从命令就是
I will follow your orders.

131
00:13:05,250 --> 00:13:06,730
胡大人不必解释
There's no need to explain.

132
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:12,140
"Lu Tong Second Commander of Zhejiang"

133
00:13:09,290 --> 00:13:12,720
胡大人只是想让俞将军稍事休息而已
Commander Hu only wants you to rest up.

134
00:13:14,830 --> 00:13:16,350
卢将军 我们走吧
Let's go, General Lu!

135
00:13:16,660 --> 00:13:17,520
喝酒去
Let's go for a drink.

136
00:13:17,580 --> 00:13:18,850
好 请
Sure! After you...

137
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:35,890
元敬
Jiguang,

138
00:13:36,790 --> 00:13:39,940
先锋的重任就交给你
I'm making you the vanguard.

139
00:13:41,040 --> 00:13:43,270
戚继光必全力以赴
I'll do my best.

140
00:14:07,830 --> 00:14:11,980
"A few months ago"

141
00:14:13,250 --> 00:14:17,180
"Longshang, Cixi"

142
00:14:42,950 --> 00:14:44,060
谁叫你开炮
Who asked you to open fire?

143
00:14:44,830 --> 00:14:46,020
攻呀
Charge!

144
00:14:56,910 --> 00:14:58,440
谁给跑 给我站住
Who's running away? Stop!

145
00:15:03,790 --> 00:15:05,390
把敌人的头拿回来
Bring me their heads.

146
00:15:24,290 --> 00:15:25,020
大家冲呀
Charge!

147
00:15:25,910 --> 00:15:26,690
不要后退
Don't back off!

148
00:15:30,750 --> 00:15:32,480
危险 退后
Watch out! Fall back!

149
00:15:35,580 --> 00:15:37,430
撤退
Retreat!

150
00:15:42,950 --> 00:15:47,860
"Hu Zongxian Residence"

151
00:15:54,830 --> 00:15:56,150
数量核示清楚
Count them carefully!

152
00:16:00,250 --> 00:16:01,400
胡大人
Commander!

153
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:07,100
元敬你来了
Jiguang,

154
00:16:07,160 --> 00:16:08,110
来来来
come here

155
00:16:10,830 --> 00:16:12,150
你们调兵遣将
You deploy the troops,

156
00:16:12,330 --> 00:16:15,180
我呢只懂调钱调财
I deploy the money.

157
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:18,350
这浙江如今是什么都缺呀
Zhejiang is short of supplies right now.

158
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:20,720
坐吧
Have a seat.

159
00:16:32,250 --> 00:16:34,520
龙山所雁门岭之役
At the battle of Yanmen Ridge,

160
00:16:34,870 --> 00:16:36,730
我们以数倍倭寇的兵力
we outnumbered the pirates,

161
00:16:36,910 --> 00:16:38,640
只和他们打个平手
but we only managed a tie.

162
00:16:38,950 --> 00:16:40,730
怎么还敢报功呢
We dared not report a victory.

163
00:16:41,450 --> 00:16:43,270
不曲道以媚时
Never violate the rules of life to suit the time.

164
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:46,430
不诡行以邀名
Never commit treachery to attain fame.

165
00:16:48,330 --> 00:16:51,890
这个道理世人皆懂
It is easier said than done.

166
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:55,820
可我却做不到
I, for one, cannot do it.

167
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:01,400
你可知道
Do you know

168
00:17:01,870 --> 00:17:05,180
此时此刻有多少双眼睛在盯着我们吗
all eyes are on us right now?

169
00:17:06,330 --> 00:17:09,610
我们如今只能赢 不能输
We can't afford to lose.

170
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:12,940
输了 朝廷震动天下权变
A defeat will shake the Imperial Court to its core.

171
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:14,520
所以这一战
This is a battle

172
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:16,310
你只能赢
you must win.

173
00:17:21,250 --> 00:17:22,850
你三箭定胜负
The three arrows you shot

174
00:17:23,450 --> 00:17:25,100
已成军中美颂
became a legend in the Army.

175
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:29,310
大家都指 能在你手下作战
Everyone hopes to fight under your command.

176
00:17:29,950 --> 00:17:31,900
心中会有安稳之心呀
They feel safe.

177
00:17:32,660 --> 00:17:35,110
败就败在求安稳之心呀
But this is also our handicap.

178
00:17:35,410 --> 00:17:36,110
大人
Commander,

179
00:17:36,410 --> 00:17:38,560
当兵的哪有求安稳的
soldiers should not expect to be safe.

180
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:43,230
大人 我请许重组新军
Please allow me to set up a new army.

181
00:17:43,290 --> 00:17:44,770
请大人批许
I need your approval.

182
00:17:59,080 --> 00:18:01,180
杀贼方是当务之急
Fighting the pirates is your top priority.

183
00:18:01,450 --> 00:18:03,270
怎么能去练兵呢
You have no time to train soldiers.

184
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:05,150
你专心杀敌就好了
Concentrate on taking out the enemies.

185
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:07,270
可是他们见到倭寇就跑
The sight of pirates make them flee.

186
00:18:07,870 --> 00:18:09,730
仗还没打就已经败了
The battle is lost before it began.

187
00:18:09,910 --> 00:18:11,560
大人你说这仗怎么打
How can we fight like that?

188
00:18:11,580 --> 00:18:14,610
有你在 大家一定会变的
They can change with you in command.

189
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:18,310
这正是我从山东把你请过来的目的
This is why I brought you from Shandong.

190
00:18:18,700 --> 00:18:21,480
要你 杀敌邀功
I need you to wipe out the pirates.

191
00:18:21,870 --> 00:18:26,060
我们可以杀敌 练兵两不担误同时进行
I can kill pirates and train soldiers at the same time.

192
00:18:26,580 --> 00:18:29,280
练新兵 练新兵 元敬
Train soldiers...

193
00:18:29,700 --> 00:18:31,230
浙江兵怕倭寇
Zhejiang soldiers are scared of pirates.

194
00:18:31,870 --> 00:18:34,820
已经是个定局了 练不了的
That's a fact. What more can you do?

195
00:18:34,950 --> 00:18:35,810
大人
Commander,

196
00:18:36,250 --> 00:18:37,820
十室之邑必有忠信
you can find someone faithful even in a town with 10 houses.

197
00:18:37,830 --> 00:18:39,810
堂堂全浙 岂无材勇
There must be someone courageous in Zhejiang.

198
00:18:40,080 --> 00:18:42,150
况且由我来自行训练
If I'm in charge of the training,

199
00:18:42,500 --> 00:18:46,020
更可以省掉不少请客兵的军费
you can save the money on hiring Guest Troops.

200
00:18:55,410 --> 00:18:56,390
好呀
Very well!

201
00:18:58,580 --> 00:18:59,520
好呀
Very well!

202
00:19:00,950 --> 00:19:02,520
好呀 元敬
Very well, Jiguang.

203
00:19:02,950 --> 00:19:06,260
难得你愿意费神再去训练新军
If you take the trouble to train a new army,

204
00:19:06,370 --> 00:19:08,270
我怎么能不支持呢
I must show my support.

205
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:11,190
只是雁门岭一役
About the battle of Yanmen Ridge,

206
00:19:11,580 --> 00:19:13,060
我必须要报军功
we must report this extraordinary feat

207
00:19:14,540 --> 00:19:17,480
全歼倭寇 就这么定了
of wiping out the pirates.

208
00:19:26,450 --> 00:19:30,390
上 上
Go!

209
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:40,640
哥
Jiguang!

210
00:19:40,870 --> 00:19:42,270
我们日日闹了好几天了
We have been doing this for days.

211
00:19:42,410 --> 00:19:43,810
什么时候打呀？
When are we going to fight?

212
00:19:44,000 --> 00:19:45,400
你有方法攻上去吗
You have a better plan?

213
00:19:45,790 --> 00:19:47,860
这有什么办法 冲呀
What plan? Just charge ahead!

214
00:19:48,540 --> 00:19:49,810
将军每天来
The General comes here every day

215
00:19:50,290 --> 00:19:52,390
就想破敌之法
trying to think of a plan.

216
00:19:53,080 --> 00:19:54,020
不攻不打
We don't attack or fight,

217
00:19:54,330 --> 00:19:55,930
不就让敌人松懈嘛
because we want the enemy to let their guard down.

218
00:19:56,660 --> 00:19:59,520
楼楠 你又猜到我在想什么了
Lou Nan, you can always read my mind.

219
00:19:59,910 --> 00:20:00,980
这太可怕了
That's too scary!

220
00:20:01,750 --> 00:20:02,720
回去吧
Let's go back.

221
00:20:05,580 --> 00:20:08,230
明军又不攻进来了
The Ming Army did not launch an attack.

222
00:20:08,950 --> 00:20:12,060
是不敢战吗
Are they afraid to fight?

223
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:17,770
三十不到已被奉为名将
He made a name for himself before he turned 30.

224
00:20:18,660 --> 00:20:20,360
这人是个奇才
Don't lower your guard.

225
00:20:22,370 --> 00:20:24,190
别掉以轻心
This man is a genius.

226
00:20:25,250 --> 00:20:27,320
回营休息 收起将旗
Let's return to camp and take down the banners.

227
00:20:27,410 --> 00:20:28,270
是
Aye!

228
00:20:41,370 --> 00:20:42,020
将军
General!

229
00:20:42,290 --> 00:20:43,230
开始下雨了
It's raining!

230
00:20:45,830 --> 00:20:46,350
哥
Jiguang,

231
00:20:46,580 --> 00:20:48,150
这仗什么都准备好了
everything is ready.

232
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:49,060
现在下着雨
Shouldn't we

233
00:20:49,080 --> 00:20:51,230
我们不就是应该趁着下雨夜袭嘛？
launch the attack in the rain?

234
00:20:52,830 --> 00:20:54,060
趁着下雨夜袭
In the rain?

235
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:54,850
是呀
Yes!

236
00:20:57,790 --> 00:20:58,890
你能想得出来
If you can think of it,

237
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:00,350
倭寇也能想得到
so can the pirates.

238
00:21:01,290 --> 00:21:02,270
去休息吧
Go get some rest.

239
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:05,350
这说是休息
You should

240
00:21:05,370 --> 00:21:07,690
不是应该回军营休息吗 哥
return to camp.

241
00:21:11,950 --> 00:21:13,850
行行行 休息休息
Alright... I'll get some rest.

242
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,900
你哥向来以奇兵取胜
Your brother is known to take his enemies by surprise.

243
00:21:18,620 --> 00:21:19,440
等吧
Let's wait!

244
00:21:23,290 --> 00:21:24,190
听命
Listen up...

245
00:21:24,750 --> 00:21:26,020
原地休息
get some rest!

246
00:21:32,620 --> 00:21:37,560
小心明军趁着下雨夜袭
Beware of an attack in the rain at night.

247
00:21:38,120 --> 00:21:39,940
大家提高警觉
Be vigilant!

248
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:43,690
听清楚没有 啊
Did you hear me?

249
00:21:48,120 --> 00:21:49,440
真多想法
What a pain!

250
00:21:50,450 --> 00:21:51,810
好吧
Very well!

251
00:21:52,500 --> 00:21:54,190
别吵了 在怕什么
What are you afraid of?

252
00:22:15,620 --> 00:22:16,440
还给你
Here...

253
00:22:18,200 --> 00:22:20,430
安心吧 我没碰过她
Relax! I didn't lay a hand on her!

254
00:22:25,870 --> 00:22:27,100
我是武士
I'm a samurai,

255
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:29,650
跟你们不一样
unlike the lot of you.

256
00:22:37,620 --> 00:22:39,440
木幡 喝酒
Drink up, Kohata!

257
00:22:55,410 --> 00:22:56,560
都睡着了
They're asleep.

258
00:22:58,830 --> 00:22:59,810
太好了
Excellent

259
00:23:01,620 --> 00:23:04,430
通知俞将军 只要一听到炮声
Tell General Yu to meet me in the mountain

260
00:23:04,450 --> 00:23:05,980
就上山和我们会合
when he hears the cannon.

261
00:23:06,450 --> 00:23:08,230
把大家叫醒 马上出发
Wake up the troops, we're moving out.

262
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:11,110
小声点
Keep it down!

263
00:23:33,450 --> 00:23:34,180
什么事
What's going on?

264
00:23:34,950 --> 00:23:35,850
拉…
Pull...

265
00:23:43,580 --> 00:23:45,810
突袭 被突袭了
A raid! We've been attacked!

266
00:23:48,410 --> 00:23:49,140
上呀
Charge!

267
00:23:49,160 --> 00:23:50,110
冲
go

268
00:23:52,870 --> 00:23:53,940
糟了
We're in trouble!

269
00:23:54,250 --> 00:23:55,070
攻呀
Run!

270
00:23:57,790 --> 00:23:59,640
攻呀
Charge!

271
00:24:09,080 --> 00:24:10,100
跟我走 来
Follow me!

272
00:24:10,160 --> 00:24:10,610
我不去
I'm not going!

273
00:24:32,700 --> 00:24:33,730
给我追
After them!

274
00:24:35,750 --> 00:24:37,270
第一部队 出击
Unit 1, charge!

275
00:24:37,950 --> 00:24:39,060
出发
Let's move out!

276
00:24:39,450 --> 00:24:40,310
大人
Sir!

277
00:24:40,910 --> 00:24:43,360
明军已突破我们的防线
The Ming Army broke through our line of defense.

278
00:24:43,540 --> 00:24:44,810
那么快
Already?

279
00:24:45,450 --> 00:24:48,030
那个将军果然厉害
That general is formidable indeed.

280
00:24:48,290 --> 00:24:49,110
老师
Sensei,

281
00:24:49,500 --> 00:24:51,100
我们过去帮忙吧
let's go give them a hand.

282
00:24:52,580 --> 00:24:55,940
已攻上了寨门就守不住了
They're at the front gate. We can't hold them back.

283
00:24:56,250 --> 00:24:58,600
我们不会输给明军
We won't let them beat us.

284
00:24:59,750 --> 00:25:05,150
明国是一头大象 不能硬碰的
The Ming Dynasty is like an elephant; you can't take it head on.

285
00:25:05,330 --> 00:25:08,260
只打必胜的 不打平手的
I want a win, not a tie.

286
00:25:08,290 --> 00:25:10,890
即使打胜但有损伤我也不愿意
But not a win at the expense of casualties.

287
00:25:14,330 --> 00:25:15,480
还是退吧
We should retreat.

288
00:25:15,750 --> 00:25:17,730
大人 退吗
Are you sure?

289
00:25:18,370 --> 00:25:19,900
谁愿意殿后
Who's willing to bring up the rear?

290
00:25:20,500 --> 00:25:22,690
当然是我
Me, of course!

291
00:25:23,500 --> 00:25:24,570
拜托你
Thank you!

292
00:25:24,580 --> 00:25:25,180
是
Yes!

293
00:25:25,750 --> 00:25:26,900
准备收拾行装
Let's pack up and go!

294
00:25:27,040 --> 00:25:27,730
明白
Aye!

295
00:25:27,870 --> 00:25:28,520
去吧
Go!

296
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:29,890
撤退
Retreat!

297
00:25:30,370 --> 00:25:31,820
撤退吧
Come on!

298
00:25:36,120 --> 00:25:36,940
少主
Master Yamagawa,

299
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:39,690
可以帮我忙吗
can you give me a hand?

300
00:25:40,200 --> 00:25:41,230
我很乐意
My pleasure.

301
00:25:47,910 --> 00:25:50,860
撤退 撤退
Retreat!

302
00:25:51,040 --> 00:25:52,190
这边走
This way!

303
00:25:54,160 --> 00:25:55,110
你们要走
You must leave.

304
00:25:55,790 --> 00:25:58,360
不舍得也要快点撤退
We must go even if you don't want to.

305
00:26:29,950 --> 00:26:30,810
俞将军
General Yu!

306
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:31,820
请进
Please come in.

307
00:26:32,620 --> 00:26:33,650
佩服了
Impressive!

308
00:26:34,870 --> 00:26:35,520
佩服了
I'm impressed!

309
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:40,940
楼楠
Lou Nan!

310
00:26:41,370 --> 00:26:41,850
将军
General!

311
00:26:41,870 --> 00:26:42,690
怎么回事
What is it?

312
00:26:42,790 --> 00:26:43,770
贼兵已经走了
The pirates are gone.

313
00:26:44,450 --> 00:26:45,480
地上很多碎银
They left behind scraps of silver.

314
00:26:46,250 --> 00:26:47,900
将士们都在四处搜银
The soldiers are busy picking them up.

315
00:26:51,040 --> 00:26:52,610
哥 这村民要见你
Jiguang, this villager wants to see you.

316
00:26:53,040 --> 00:26:54,890
将军 将军
General...

317
00:26:55,080 --> 00:26:56,230
起来说话
Please get UP!

318
00:26:56,620 --> 00:26:59,190
将军 还有很多村民被锁在旧房里面
Other villagers are still locked up.

319
00:26:59,290 --> 00:27:01,440
将军你快去救救他们吧 将军
Please rescue them quickly, General.

320
00:27:01,500 --> 00:27:02,440
带我去
Take me there!

321
00:27:06,120 --> 00:27:06,690
就在这
Over here!

322
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:12,060
哥
Jiguang!

323
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,430
戚将军来救我们了
General Qi is hereto save us.

324
00:27:13,580 --> 00:27:15,100
大家快出来 快出
Come out, all of you!

325
00:27:15,120 --> 00:27:16,690
戚将军来救我们了
General Qi is hereto save us.

326
00:27:16,700 --> 00:27:17,730
快出来
Come out!

327
00:27:18,620 --> 00:27:20,070
谢谢将军
Thank you, General Qi!

328
00:27:22,040 --> 00:27:23,560
好好好 起来吧
Please get UP!

329
00:27:29,500 --> 00:27:30,270
抓住戚继光
Grab Qi!

330
00:28:06,370 --> 00:28:07,470
杀
Kill!

331
00:28:24,910 --> 00:28:25,610
撤呀
Let's go!

332
00:28:26,450 --> 00:28:27,180
撤呀
Let's go!

333
00:28:36,910 --> 00:28:37,480
蹲下
Get down!

334
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:39,070
准备好
Ready!

335
00:28:40,540 --> 00:28:41,940
开炮
Fire!

336
00:28:54,910 --> 00:28:55,770
哥
Jiguang!

337
00:28:57,660 --> 00:28:59,060
救人 快救人
Get them out! Hurry!

338
00:28:59,660 --> 00:29:00,440
哥
Jiguang!

339
00:29:01,080 --> 00:29:02,430
救人 快
Help them...

340
00:29:07,660 --> 00:29:08,980
哥
Jiguang!

341
00:29:14,370 --> 00:29:15,770
你没事吧 哥
Are you alright?

342
00:29:15,790 --> 00:29:16,690
我没事
I'm fine.

343
00:29:16,950 --> 00:29:17,730
救人
Help them...

344
00:29:18,450 --> 00:29:19,060
救人
Help them...

345
00:29:20,580 --> 00:29:21,520
贼兵当中
Among the pirates,

346
00:29:22,660 --> 00:29:24,520
大部份都是因为海禁
majority of them were Han Chinese dispossessed by the sea ban

347
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:26,890
而投靠王直的汉人
and sought refuge with Wang Zhi.

348
00:29:28,290 --> 00:29:30,610
你是说我们打的不是倭寇
You're saying they are not Japanese?

349
00:29:31,000 --> 00:29:32,020
也有浪人
They include Japanese ronins.

350
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:34,430
但最有战斗力的
But those with genuine combat prowess

351
00:29:34,790 --> 00:29:38,270
而是一群配备精良的倭兵
are well equipped Japanese soldiers.

352
00:29:38,830 --> 00:29:39,810
倭兵
Japanese soldiers?

353
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:42,560
我们就是碰到他们
That's who we're dealing with.

354
00:29:42,910 --> 00:29:43,610
很少见
They're rare.

355
00:29:43,620 --> 00:29:44,900
将军 胡大人来了
General, Commander Hu is here.

356
00:29:46,330 --> 00:29:47,230
又来了
Again?

357
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:51,220
恭喜两位将军
Congratulations,

358
00:29:51,830 --> 00:29:53,680
胡大人带来了上好的黄酒
Commander Hu brought the best yellow wine

359
00:29:53,950 --> 00:29:55,150
跟大家庆祝一下
to celebrate with you.

360
00:29:55,620 --> 00:29:58,020
胡大人为何带锦衣卫进来
Why did you bring the Imperial Secret Service with you?

361
00:30:00,950 --> 00:30:04,560
侍中罗嘉宾几个人正要上书弹劾你
Luo Jiabin and his lot intend to impeach you

362
00:30:05,580 --> 00:30:06,930
说你放走倭寇
for letting the pirates get away.

363
00:30:07,500 --> 00:30:08,720
指你通敌
They said you colluded with them.

364
00:30:09,450 --> 00:30:10,480
我没通敌
I did not!

365
00:30:12,830 --> 00:30:14,400
我当然心里清楚了
I know.

366
00:30:15,500 --> 00:30:18,020
我已经上报朝廷报捷了
I already reported your victory.

367
00:30:18,870 --> 00:30:21,730
在朝廷尚未收到捷报之前
But before my report reaches the Court,

368
00:30:23,080 --> 00:30:24,520
你先要留在家里
you are to stay home

369
00:30:25,410 --> 00:30:26,480
听候发落
pending your sentence.

370
00:30:32,040 --> 00:30:33,020
俞将军
General Yu,

371
00:30:33,870 --> 00:30:34,820
抱歉了
I'm sorry!

372
00:30:37,750 --> 00:30:38,640
没问题
No problem!

373
00:30:46,250 --> 00:30:47,820
我会尽力周旋的
I will do my best to intercede.

374
00:30:49,160 --> 00:30:50,360
不要只抓俞将军
Don't just arrest General Yu.

375
00:30:50,540 --> 00:30:51,890
要抓两个一起抓
Put me under arrest as well.

376
00:30:55,120 --> 00:30:56,150
朝廷有命
I have my orders.

377
00:30:56,620 --> 00:30:58,070
俞将军出师不利
General Yu failed his expedition

378
00:30:58,500 --> 00:30:59,690
纵寇南逃
and allowed the pirates to flee to the South.

379
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:01,770
需暂时交锦衣卫收押
The Imperial Secret Service will take him into custody.

380
00:31:04,120 --> 00:31:05,850
俞将军 得罪了 请
Pardon us, General! This way.

381
00:31:05,870 --> 00:31:06,720
明白
I understand.

382
00:31:07,080 --> 00:31:07,770
俞将军
General Yu...

383
00:31:10,410 --> 00:31:11,140
没事的
I'll be fine.

384
00:31:23,450 --> 00:31:25,680
这不是我能决定的
It wasn't my decision to make.

385
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:48,060
当官当得这么委屈
This is so unfair.

386
00:31:48,700 --> 00:31:49,930
那就不要当了
You should quit.

387
00:31:51,620 --> 00:31:53,270
房子多太 俸禄多少
Tiny house, small salary...

388
00:31:53,290 --> 00:31:54,480
我又不稀罕
Who cares?

389
00:31:55,580 --> 00:31:58,060
那姓胡的声名狼藉
Hu Zongxian is notorious.

390
00:31:58,450 --> 00:31:59,810
你在他手下
Working for him,

391
00:32:00,120 --> 00:32:02,730
败是坏事 成也可能是坏事
win or lose, you're doomed.

392
00:32:05,790 --> 00:32:07,110
我这妇人之见
This is just my humble opinion.

393
00:32:07,450 --> 00:32:08,770
听还是不听
Whether or not you want to listen,

394
00:32:09,750 --> 00:32:10,720
随你
it's up to you.

395
00:32:22,660 --> 00:32:25,020
夫人讲的每一句话都有道理
You make perfect sense.

396
00:32:26,200 --> 00:32:27,980
可是倭寇大敌当前
But the enemy is at the gate,

397
00:32:28,580 --> 00:32:29,850
我又怎能不理
I can't just walk away.

398
00:32:31,450 --> 00:32:32,930
那就天下大事
It's a state matter;

399
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:34,980
可是只有你一个人可担当
you can't do this alone.

400
00:32:43,370 --> 00:32:45,070
不是还心中郁闷吗？
I thought you're depressed.

401
00:32:45,410 --> 00:32:46,980
怎么不规矩起来了
Why this disorderly behavior?

402
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:49,150
我怎么不规矩呢
What do you mean?

403
00:32:50,910 --> 00:32:52,640
夫妻行周公之礼
Sexual intercourse between husband and wife

404
00:32:54,080 --> 00:32:56,100
是天经地义之事
is the most natural and proper thing to do.

405
00:32:58,080 --> 00:32:59,770
又想拿礼法压我吗
Don't throw the book in my face again.

406
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:01,310
我哪敢
I wouldn't dare.

407
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:05,440
有什么不敢的
Of course you would.

408
00:33:05,910 --> 00:33:07,610
你不是天下无敌吗
You're invincible.

409
00:33:11,120 --> 00:33:13,480
夫人才是真正的天下无敌
You're the invincible one.

410
00:33:48,250 --> 00:33:49,770
我们的盾挡不住呀
Our shields are not tough enough.

411
00:33:50,910 --> 00:33:51,940
再想想办法
We'll think of something.

412
00:34:02,910 --> 00:34:05,310
这就是毛海峰的倭刀
This is Mao Haifeng's sword.

413
00:34:06,660 --> 00:34:07,360
哥
Here...

414
00:34:07,620 --> 00:34:09,190
这刀给你当配刀吧
You can use this.

415
00:34:12,370 --> 00:34:13,350
那可不行
Absolutely not!

416
00:34:14,250 --> 00:34:17,190
堂堂大明将军拿一把倭刀
A Ming general using a Japanese sword

417
00:34:17,330 --> 00:34:19,020
岂不长了别人的威风
is bad for morale.

418
00:34:19,750 --> 00:34:21,980
不过这刀倒是挺锋利的
No doubt this is a good sword.

419
00:34:22,330 --> 00:34:25,060
是啊 想不到如此锐利
I'm surprised it's such a trenchant sword.

420
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:28,070
应该跟我们的打造方法不一样
I think it's made differently from ours.

421
00:34:28,950 --> 00:34:29,680
继美
Jimei!

422
00:34:29,790 --> 00:34:30,610
你琢磨琢磨
Study it carefully,

423
00:34:30,830 --> 00:34:32,560
看看这刀是怎样锻成的
and find out how it's forged.

424
00:34:32,790 --> 00:34:33,390
好
Sure!

425
00:34:35,200 --> 00:34:35,850
将军
General!

426
00:34:36,330 --> 00:34:37,020
戚将军
General Qi!

427
00:34:37,370 --> 00:34:38,820
胡大人刚收到了朝廷公文
Commander Hu just received Court documents

428
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:40,820
将军于舟山岑港破敌立功
about your victory at Cengang.

429
00:34:40,910 --> 00:34:41,810
官复原职
You have been reinstated.

430
00:34:44,120 --> 00:34:44,640
好呀
Good!

431
00:34:44,790 --> 00:34:46,190
那俞大猷将军呢
What about General Yu?

432
00:34:47,160 --> 00:34:48,940
还没有俞将军复职的消息
There has been no word.

433
00:34:59,450 --> 00:34:59,980
来
Come!

434
00:35:06,410 --> 00:35:07,230
俞将军
General Yu!

435
00:35:07,790 --> 00:35:08,440
俞将军
General Yu!

436
00:35:08,450 --> 00:35:09,900
戚将军 卢将军
General Qi! General Lu!

437
00:35:10,080 --> 00:35:11,100
你们来得正好
I'm glad you're here.

438
00:35:11,580 --> 00:35:12,930
这就是我跟你们说
This is General Qi Jiguang,

439
00:35:13,160 --> 00:35:15,690
大破岑港贼兵的戚继光
who commanded the decisive victory at Cengang.

440
00:35:15,700 --> 00:35:17,020
久仰久仰
We have heard so much about you.

441
00:35:18,500 --> 00:35:19,570
三位将军慢用
Enjoy!

442
00:35:20,500 --> 00:35:22,190
都已经官复原职了
You have been reinstated.

443
00:35:23,250 --> 00:35:24,470
还有什么忧心的
What are you worried about?

444
00:35:26,450 --> 00:35:27,350
没想到
I didn't expect

445
00:35:27,370 --> 00:35:30,190
俞将军坐牢也能坐得这么轻松
you'd be so relaxed in jail.

446
00:35:30,750 --> 00:35:31,900
这些年来
Over the years,

447
00:35:32,040 --> 00:35:35,310
在战场上牺牲的兄弟你知道有多少
have you any idea how many men were lost in battle?

448
00:35:36,830 --> 00:35:38,980
我不过在这里等候发落
I'm just waiting for my sentence.

449
00:35:40,000 --> 00:35:42,440
还有一些兄弟可以切磋武功
I can still practice with my men.

450
00:35:43,620 --> 00:35:44,770
有什么可怨呢
What's there to complain about?

451
00:35:45,450 --> 00:35:47,230
俞将军抗倭多年
You have fought the pirates for years

452
00:35:47,410 --> 00:35:48,390
功劳不少
and earned great merit.

453
00:35:48,540 --> 00:35:50,190
难道不觉得委屈吗
Don't you feel aggrieved?

454
00:35:52,200 --> 00:35:53,480
我战倭多年
Yes, I fought pirates for years.

455
00:35:54,120 --> 00:35:55,400
倭患除了吗
Have they been wiped out?

456
00:35:57,160 --> 00:35:58,060
我惭愧呀
I feel ashamed.

457
00:35:59,200 --> 00:36:00,400
凭什么委屈
I have no right to feel aggrieved.

458
00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:03,770
我们在前线以血奋战
We shed our blood on the frontline

459
00:36:03,950 --> 00:36:06,680
而那些昏官却在背后说三道四
while those fatuous officials badmouth us behind our backs,

460
00:36:06,870 --> 00:36:08,570
还把责任推到您身上
and try to pin the blame on you.

461
00:36:09,250 --> 00:36:11,070
您不觉得不安吗？
You don't find that unsettling?

462
00:36:11,160 --> 00:36:12,690
你是说胡大人
You mean Commander Hu?

463
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:17,350
他为官难啊
It hasn't been easy for him.

464
00:36:17,790 --> 00:36:20,480
若不是胡大人和徐渭大人
Commander Hu and Xu Wei

465
00:36:21,080 --> 00:36:23,430
他们用各种方法保住俞某
did their best to cover up for me.

466
00:36:24,370 --> 00:36:28,520
可能俞某已经跟张经大人一样身首异处了
Or else I would have been beheaded like Zhang Jing.

467
00:36:29,290 --> 00:36:33,020
胡宗宪和严嵩的干儿子赵文华一伙
Hu Zongxian colluded with Yan Song's godson Zhao Wenhua

468
00:36:33,500 --> 00:36:34,900
为他们出谋划策
and did their bidding.

469
00:36:35,620 --> 00:36:37,190
不仅取代了张经大人
He replaced Commander Zhang Jing

470
00:36:37,330 --> 00:36:38,520
更害死了他
and had him executed.

471
00:36:38,830 --> 00:36:39,900
难道是假的吗
None of that is true?

472
00:36:41,370 --> 00:36:44,020
胡大人不跟赵文华周旋
If Commander Hu didn't kiss up to Zhao Wenhua,

473
00:36:44,540 --> 00:36:45,980
你我人头能保
you and I are probably dead by now.

474
00:36:47,160 --> 00:36:48,390
我们何来军饷
Where do you think the army provisions came from?

475
00:36:49,000 --> 00:36:50,480
何来战倭的机会
We'd never get the chance to fight pirates.

476
00:36:50,910 --> 00:36:52,140
胡大人争取的
He bargained for a thankless job

477
00:36:52,540 --> 00:36:56,140
是一个连打胜仗都会被杀头的苦差
that could have him beheaded even if he had won.

478
00:36:56,700 --> 00:36:59,030
你说他这是何苦呢
Why should he bother?

479
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:04,640
我这命 原来就是胡大人捡回来的
Commander Hu saved my life.

480
00:37:06,080 --> 00:37:07,060
无憾了
I have no complaints.

481
00:37:08,410 --> 00:37:09,690
我们习武之人
As a martial artist,

482
00:37:10,540 --> 00:37:12,230
问心无愧便是了
I'm satisfied as long as I have a clear conscience.

483
00:37:15,540 --> 00:37:17,310
能有你来接这担子
I'm also pleased

484
00:37:17,790 --> 00:37:18,560
我欣慰
that you will now take over this burden.

485
00:37:18,750 --> 00:37:20,070
来 喝一杯
Here... have a drink with me.

486
00:37:33,450 --> 00:37:35,980
胡大人会尽力让我出去的
Commander Hu will get me out.

487
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:38,940
俞大哥
Brother Yu,

488
00:37:39,290 --> 00:37:41,560
小弟想向您问一件事
can I ask you something?

489
00:37:41,580 --> 00:37:42,270
什么
What?

490
00:37:42,410 --> 00:37:43,940
早闻大哥的棍法
I was told your skill with the staff

491
00:37:44,290 --> 00:37:46,230
威震少林独步天下
is outstanding in Shaolin and unmatched in the world.

492
00:37:46,660 --> 00:37:47,690
上次在岑港
I had a glimpse of it

493
00:37:48,160 --> 00:37:49,640
有幸得以一见
last time in Cengang,

494
00:37:49,830 --> 00:37:52,060
今日想再次请教
I'd like to take another look.

495
00:37:52,080 --> 00:37:53,100
好
Very well!

496
00:38:01,330 --> 00:38:03,520
一寸长 一寸强
An inch longer, an inch stronger.

497
00:38:06,660 --> 00:38:09,110
寸短寸险
An inch shorter, an inch deadlier.

498
00:38:50,290 --> 00:38:51,230
再来
Again!

499
00:39:55,620 --> 00:39:57,440
戚将军 卢将军
General Qi! General Lu!

500
00:39:57,660 --> 00:39:58,480
戚将军
General Qi!

501
00:40:00,500 --> 00:40:01,720
卢将军 戚将军
General Lu! General Qi!

502
00:40:02,500 --> 00:40:03,470
就在这里说
Stay where you are.

503
00:40:03,750 --> 00:40:05,350
得知诸位将军出外勘察
I heard you were going on an inspection tour.

504
00:40:05,540 --> 00:40:07,310
胡大人特派郑某同行协力
Commander Hu sent me to assist you.

505
00:40:07,500 --> 00:40:08,690
请诸位多多指教
I have so much to learn from you.

506
00:40:08,700 --> 00:40:09,770
多多指教
So much indeed.

507
00:40:10,290 --> 00:40:11,940
你这等于来监视我们的吗
Learn from us? You're here to spy on us.

508
00:40:12,200 --> 00:40:12,850
不不不
No...

509
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:14,570
胡大人指小人懂点笔墨
Because I can read and write,

510
00:40:14,790 --> 00:40:16,730
特意让小人来协助戚将军的
Commander Hu wanted me to assist General Qi.

511
00:40:20,750 --> 00:40:21,520
有劳了
Thank you.

512
00:40:21,830 --> 00:40:22,730
上马了
Let's go!

513
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:24,320
行了 将军您坐好
Sit tight, General.

514
00:40:27,160 --> 00:40:28,730
好了 可以出发了
We can go now.

515
00:40:31,580 --> 00:40:32,270
嫂子
Sister!

516
00:40:40,700 --> 00:40:41,430
好啊
Excellent

517
00:40:43,910 --> 00:40:44,560
夫人
Wait up...

518
00:40:45,330 --> 00:40:45,900
夫人
Wait up!

519
00:40:46,700 --> 00:40:47,480
夫人
Hey...

520
00:40:47,910 --> 00:40:48,810
你怎么了
What's wrong?

521
00:40:50,370 --> 00:40:51,270
怎么了
What's wrong?

522
00:40:51,870 --> 00:40:53,570
你去视察地方要几天几夜
You'll be gone for several days.

523
00:40:53,660 --> 00:40:55,190
不带我去也是应该的
Naturally you don't want to bring me along.

524
00:40:55,450 --> 00:40:56,350
谁说的
Says who?

525
00:40:56,410 --> 00:40:57,390
谁说不带你去呀
Who says I'm not bringing you?

526
00:40:57,450 --> 00:40:58,060
那马呢
Then where's my horse?

527
00:40:58,250 --> 00:40:59,020
在备呀
We're getting it ready.

528
00:40:59,160 --> 00:40:59,860
在备
Getting it ready?

529
00:41:03,700 --> 00:41:05,480
夫人 你急什么
What's your hurry?

530
00:41:05,950 --> 00:41:08,400
我怎么舍得把你一个人扔在家里呢
Why would I leave you behind?

531
00:41:10,660 --> 00:41:11,690
我舍得吗
You think I'd want that?

532
00:41:17,700 --> 00:41:18,680
快 快 快了
Hurry...

533
00:41:20,700 --> 00:41:21,600
马备好了
The horse is ready.

534
00:41:25,830 --> 00:41:26,350
哥
Jiguang!

535
00:41:26,790 --> 00:41:27,730
戚夫人 早
Morning, Madam Qi!

536
00:41:29,750 --> 00:41:30,640
卢将军 早
Morning, General Lu!

537
00:41:31,250 --> 00:41:33,600
刚才戚将军正跟我说
General Qi told me just now

538
00:41:34,120 --> 00:41:36,190
等候戚夫人一起上路呢
we're waiting for you.

539
00:41:37,160 --> 00:41:38,610
让卢将军久等了
Sorry to keep you waiting.

540
00:41:45,160 --> 00:41:45,940
夫人
Allow me...

541
00:42:18,250 --> 00:42:19,600
美女
Hey pretty lady!

542
00:42:22,500 --> 00:42:24,150
你别这样
You guys, stop acting like this...

543
00:42:39,540 --> 00:42:41,110
对不起
Sorry!

544
00:42:42,870 --> 00:42:44,600
你们喝多了
You're drunk!

545
00:42:45,330 --> 00:42:46,480
看你的了
Let's see...

546
00:42:46,500 --> 00:42:48,980
不行 看我的呀
No, watch me.

547
00:42:52,950 --> 00:42:55,230
兄弟 喝多了
You're drunk, pal.

548
00:42:57,500 --> 00:42:58,470
我告诉你们
Listen up...

549
00:42:58,790 --> 00:43:00,310
我们可是戚继光的兵
We are Qi Jiguang's troops.

550
00:43:00,700 --> 00:43:01,900
专杀倭寇的
We specialize in killing pirates.

551
00:43:03,200 --> 00:43:05,480
我看 你们就是倭寇
I think you're a pirate.

552
00:43:06,370 --> 00:43:07,190
兄弟们
Brothers...

553
00:43:07,580 --> 00:43:08,810
把他们全给我抓了
take them into custody!

554
00:43:25,910 --> 00:43:26,730
大哥 大哥
Brother...

555
00:43:26,750 --> 00:43:27,600
将军
General!

556
00:43:27,620 --> 00:43:29,570
就是他 就是他打我们
That's him. He beat us up.

557
00:43:29,580 --> 00:43:31,930
闭嘴 都他妈眼瞎了
Shut up! Are you blind?

558
00:43:34,330 --> 00:43:35,310
将军
General,

559
00:43:36,620 --> 00:43:38,020
这些都是你的兵
they're your troops.

560
00:43:38,580 --> 00:43:39,810
他们不是我的兵
They can't be.

561
00:43:49,200 --> 00:43:50,680
用力
Come on...

562
00:43:55,830 --> 00:43:56,680
承让 承让
Thank you...

563
00:43:56,870 --> 00:43:58,100
戚将军 佩服
Impressive, General!

564
00:43:58,200 --> 00:43:59,270
承让 承让
Thank you...

565
00:43:59,830 --> 00:44:01,100
还有没有人想试试
Anyone else?

566
00:44:01,290 --> 00:44:02,360
要不我再来一次
Let me do it again.

567
00:44:03,450 --> 00:44:04,150
算了吧你
Forget it!

568
00:44:06,200 --> 00:44:07,100
戚夫人
Madam Qi?

569
00:44:07,410 --> 00:44:09,940
戚夫人 来来来
Come on...

570
00:44:10,750 --> 00:44:11,850
戚夫人加油
Go for it, Madam Qi...

571
00:44:14,330 --> 00:44:15,520
夫人用力
Harder...

572
00:44:40,250 --> 00:44:41,600
这是什么东西呀
What is that?

573
00:44:45,790 --> 00:44:46,560
这位大哥
Excuse me...

574
00:44:47,250 --> 00:44:48,600
请问这个是怎么用的
what is this for?

575
00:44:48,950 --> 00:44:50,350
这个是脚踩上去
Put your feet inside,

576
00:44:50,580 --> 00:44:51,480
两手扶着
and hold the handle like this.

577
00:44:51,620 --> 00:44:52,770
这个叫什么
What is it called?

578
00:44:53,160 --> 00:44:54,890
这个叫泥马
A mud horse.

579
00:44:55,160 --> 00:44:57,610
在泥中可以行走自如
You can walk in the mud.

580
00:44:58,290 --> 00:44:59,190
泥马
Mud horse?

581
00:44:59,290 --> 00:45:00,230
这个有意思呀
Very interesting.

582
00:45:00,290 --> 00:45:02,390
去体验一下吧 很好玩的
Give it a try. It's a lot fun.

583
00:45:20,500 --> 00:45:22,020
怎么会有这么多人在打架
Why are these people fighting?

584
00:45:22,370 --> 00:45:23,190
是啊
Exactly!

585
00:45:25,790 --> 00:45:26,810
那边有官差呀
The magistrate is over there.

586
00:45:27,950 --> 00:45:30,180
平时就是贪生怕死 你这个混蛋
You're such a coward...

587
00:45:30,660 --> 00:45:31,640
他为什么不管
Why doesn't he stop them?

588
00:45:34,290 --> 00:45:35,980
卑职义乌县令赵大河
Generals, I'm Zhao Dahe,

589
00:45:36,000 --> 00:45:38,150
拜见戚将军 卢将军
the county magistrate of Yiwu.

590
00:45:38,370 --> 00:45:41,150
赵大人 这些村民为何打斗
Why are these people fighting?

591
00:45:41,410 --> 00:45:42,640
二位有所不知呀
You don't understand.

592
00:45:43,000 --> 00:45:44,690
义乌这地一向贫瘠
Yiwu has always been poor and barren.

593
00:45:45,000 --> 00:45:47,520
可最近有老百姓发现了一些金矿
But the folks have discovered a gold mine lately

594
00:45:47,870 --> 00:45:49,440
和一些金属的矿
along with other metal ores.

595
00:45:49,620 --> 00:45:51,320
他们称这边为八宝山
People started calling this area Treasure Hill.

596
00:45:51,750 --> 00:45:54,810
附近永康的村民一听说了 就来探矿
Villagers from Yongkang came to mine the ores

597
00:45:55,040 --> 00:45:56,980
这不 两方面就打起来了
and the parties started to fight.

598
00:45:57,450 --> 00:45:59,060
早些天还来过一次了
They came several days ago

599
00:45:59,330 --> 00:46:01,730
已经被义乌的村民给打退了
and the villagers from Yiwu fought them off.

600
00:46:02,040 --> 00:46:04,110
这两天不 又来第二次
But they keep coming back.

601
00:46:35,620 --> 00:46:36,600
胡大人
Commander!

602
00:46:51,080 --> 00:46:51,810
胡大人
Commander!

603
00:46:52,250 --> 00:46:54,440
我在义乌发现了可练之兵
I found men in Yiwu I can train.

604
00:46:55,330 --> 00:46:56,650
我正找你呢
Just the man I want.

605
00:47:01,950 --> 00:47:03,560
自己好好看看吧
Take a look at this.

606
00:47:08,500 --> 00:47:10,270
说我拉拢赵文华
It says here I kiss up to Zhao Wenhua,

607
00:47:10,790 --> 00:47:13,440
靠权术取代张经大人
replaced Zhang Jing through political trickery

608
00:47:14,290 --> 00:47:16,860
出谋献计把他害死
and eventually devised a ploy to murder him.

609
00:47:18,120 --> 00:47:19,940
都是你元敬说的话吗
Did you say that?

610
00:47:27,620 --> 00:47:31,930
若不是锦衣卫的弟兄们都被我收买了
If I didn't pay off the Imperial Secret Service

611
00:47:34,080 --> 00:47:36,400
这话传到赵大人的耳中
and they managed to report this to Zhen Wenhua,

612
00:47:37,370 --> 00:47:40,320
你早就和张经大人同一个下场了
you'd suffer the same fate as Zhang Jing.

613
00:47:54,370 --> 00:47:55,690
我争官是真的
No doubt I was after his position,

614
00:47:56,870 --> 00:47:58,900
但是杀死张经大人
but killing Zhang Jing

615
00:47:59,750 --> 00:48:00,850
非我之意
was not my idea.

