I'm just a little late for dinner.

827
01:02:15,450 --> 01:02:17,150
没必要把事情闹大吧
There's no need to make such a fuss.

828
01:02:18,700 --> 01:02:19,730
我闹了吗
Did I?

829
01:02:22,620 --> 01:02:24,100
戚将军家宴客
General Qi is entertaining at home.

830
01:02:24,540 --> 01:02:25,860
就不该待慢客人
We must not be rude.

831
01:02:32,370 --> 01:02:33,720
你是在跟我发脾气吗
Are you picking a fight?

832
01:02:39,540 --> 01:02:40,270
夫人
Stop it!

833
01:02:59,290 --> 01:03:00,270
先告退了
We should go.

834
01:03:00,410 --> 01:03:02,390
消消气我哥不好 他不好
It's his fault.

835
01:03:04,450 --> 01:03:05,400
先走了
I better leave.

836
01:03:12,790 --> 01:03:13,890
我跟你们说
Listen to me,

837
01:03:14,450 --> 01:03:15,730
以后戚将军的事情
from now on, General Qi's business

838
01:03:16,330 --> 01:03:17,650
就是我们大家的事情啊
is our business.

839
01:03:18,000 --> 01:03:18,820
女人呀
Women!

840
01:03:19,620 --> 01:03:21,020
是要挫她一下威风
You must put her in her place.

841
01:03:21,540 --> 01:03:24,060
你要告诉她谁才是一家之主
Let her know who's in charge.

842
01:03:24,870 --> 01:03:25,770
你要告诉她
You must tell her.

843
01:03:25,870 --> 01:03:26,940
你心狠了
Be tough.

844
01:03:27,120 --> 01:03:28,350
忍无可忍
Don't take it anymore.

845
01:03:29,160 --> 01:03:30,190
老虎
Even a tiger

846
01:03:30,910 --> 01:03:32,440
也有睡觉的时候呀
will fall asleep.

847
01:03:33,540 --> 01:03:34,690
你待她睡觉了
When she's asleep,

848
01:03:35,450 --> 01:03:37,480
拿把刀 架她脖子上
put a knife to her neck.

849
01:03:38,040 --> 01:03:39,730
叫她起来 然后再告诉她
Wake her up and tell her

850
01:03:40,580 --> 01:03:42,520
你要是还不服的话
if she refuses to obey,

851
01:03:44,000 --> 01:03:45,940
大不了先杀了你再自尽
you'll kill her.

852
01:03:46,120 --> 01:03:47,150
以振夫纲
You must subjugate her.

853
01:03:47,410 --> 01:03:48,020
好
Yes!

854
01:03:48,410 --> 01:03:51,060
大成说得好 这话说真对
Hear, hear! Dacheng is right!

855
01:03:51,080 --> 01:03:52,350
哥我们就这么办
That's what we should do.

856
01:04:34,200 --> 01:04:35,270
夫人
My dear...

857
01:04:37,910 --> 01:04:39,110
为什么拿着剑
What are you doing with the sword?

858
01:04:47,250 --> 01:04:51,020
我想杀只鸡给夫人补补身子
I want to kill a chicken for you as a tonic.

859
01:05:05,790 --> 01:05:08,970
你的剑怎么用来杀鸡呢
Your sword should not be used to kill a chicken.

860
01:05:26,000 --> 01:05:26,520
大成
Dacheng,

861
01:05:28,160 --> 01:05:29,480
谁请夫人过来的
who invited my wife?

862
01:05:29,910 --> 01:05:31,270
将军不敢自己出手
We know you couldn't do it.

863
01:05:31,500 --> 01:05:33,440
我们兄弟们愿意为你出手
We decided to do it for you.

864
01:05:34,450 --> 01:05:35,770
等一会掷杯为号
Drop the cup as our signal,

865
01:05:36,250 --> 01:05:37,850
我们几个人一起用刀架她
we'll hold her at knife point.

866
01:05:38,250 --> 01:05:39,220
你什么都不用多说
You don't need to say anything.

867
01:05:39,410 --> 01:05:40,310
我们来说就好
We'll do the talking for you.

868
01:05:40,450 --> 01:05:41,680
没事的 你放心
Don't worry. Everything will be fine.

869
01:05:41,790 --> 01:05:43,190
夫人来了来了来了
Here she comes...

870
01:05:50,330 --> 01:05:50,930
相公
Jiguang,

871
01:05:51,750 --> 01:05:52,850
有什么要紧的事呀
what's so urgent

872
01:05:53,120 --> 01:05:54,520
非得叫我现在过来
that I must come over right away?

873
01:05:58,950 --> 01:05:59,480
戚夫人
Madam Qi.

874
01:06:02,410 --> 01:06:03,060
奉茶
Serve tea.

875
01:06:10,330 --> 01:06:11,150
嫂子
Sister.

876
01:06:14,290 --> 01:06:15,270
怎么了你们
What's wrong?

877
01:06:15,500 --> 01:06:16,690
为什么都怪怪的
You're all acting weird.

878
01:06:18,620 --> 01:06:19,440
戚将军
General Qi!

879
01:06:20,830 --> 01:06:21,730
茶
Your tea...

880
01:06:53,200 --> 01:06:54,430
到底出什么事了
What's going on?

881
01:07:04,410 --> 01:07:05,360
夫人
My dear,

882
01:07:07,830 --> 01:07:10,860
想请你看看我们练兵的状况
I want you to watch our training

883
01:07:11,290 --> 01:07:12,230
给点意见
and give us some advice.

884
01:07:20,830 --> 01:07:21,900
我哪懂这些
I don't know anything about that.

885
01:07:22,620 --> 01:07:23,390
就阅兵
Just review the troops.

886
01:07:25,290 --> 01:07:25,980
阅兵
Review the troops.

887
01:07:28,950 --> 01:07:29,770
阅兵好
Good idea!

888
01:07:30,750 --> 01:07:31,600
我去准备
I'll go get ready.

889
01:07:33,040 --> 01:07:33,940
听到了
You heard him.

890
01:07:34,450 --> 01:07:35,930
阅兵
Review the troops.

891
01:07:38,160 --> 01:07:38,890
走了
Let's go.

892
01:07:39,910 --> 01:07:40,860
走了
Let's go.

893
01:07:45,290 --> 01:07:48,060
戚将军是个好榜样呀
General Qi set a good example.

894
01:07:49,910 --> 01:07:50,730
等等
Wait!

895
01:07:51,250 --> 01:07:52,350
不是这你也在记下来呀
Don't write that down!

896
01:07:52,450 --> 01:07:54,100
这是史 历史呀
It's part of history.

897
01:07:54,120 --> 01:07:57,150
什么史 你给我撕了
What history? Tear that up!

898
01:08:10,160 --> 01:08:13,390
木幡的狼人部队已出发到宁海了
Kohata's ronins already set out for Ninghai.

899
01:08:15,910 --> 01:08:19,600
才三千一百三十四人
They have 3,134 men.

900
01:08:20,120 --> 01:08:22,320
戚继光的军队不管多精良
Regardless of how effective Qi's troops are,

901
01:08:22,580 --> 01:08:25,610
将军也不用这样忧心吧
there's no need for you to worry.

902
01:08:26,080 --> 01:08:28,600
听说要当他兵的人
I heard he set strict criteria for his recruits.

903
01:08:29,080 --> 01:08:32,030
大城里生活的不收 当过官的不收
No one from the big city or has been in office.

904
01:08:32,500 --> 01:08:36,810
皮肤白的不收 胆子小的不行
No one with fair complexion, no cowards.

905
01:08:37,160 --> 01:08:40,220
胆子大又不可以
Nobody too daring either.

906
01:08:40,910 --> 01:08:42,020
这样子
Just imagine,

907
01:08:42,410 --> 01:08:45,020
这些是什么人呀
what kind of people would he end up with?

908
01:08:46,660 --> 01:08:49,190
就是笨的人呀
Fools!

909
01:08:50,040 --> 01:08:53,810
不笨的不敢带呢
He'll end up commanding fools.

910
01:08:58,200 --> 01:08:59,900
岑港之战
At the battle of Cengang,

911
01:09:00,290 --> 01:09:02,610
我们是能够完全打败他们
we have the ability to defeat them.

912
01:09:03,000 --> 01:09:05,480
但老师却不让我们继续应战
But Sensei won't let us engage them.

913
01:09:05,870 --> 01:09:09,180
如果那个时候我们继续应战
Had we done that back then,

914
01:09:09,540 --> 01:09:12,480
我们今天根本就不用担心戚继光
we wouldn't have to worry about Qi today.

915
01:09:14,250 --> 01:09:19,060
少主你是在批评我吗
Are you criticizing me?

916
01:09:24,330 --> 01:09:25,900
我不明白
I don't understand.

917
01:09:26,750 --> 01:09:29,070
我们结集了两万大军
We have 20,000 men.

918
01:09:29,540 --> 01:09:32,690
只要直接进攻台州
If we attack Taizhou directly,

919
01:09:33,330 --> 01:09:36,280
到时候戚继光一定跟我们对战
Qi will have to engage us

920
01:09:36,500 --> 01:09:38,650
然后把他击败就可以了
and we can defeat him.

921
01:09:39,660 --> 01:09:41,360
如今却兵分三路
Why split the Army three ways?

922
01:09:41,700 --> 01:09:44,530
同时攻击宁海台州又有什么意义呢
What's the use of attacking Ninghai and Taizhou simultaneously?

923
01:09:47,120 --> 01:09:49,480
意义是在于必胜
To ensure a sure win.

924
01:09:51,290 --> 01:09:54,110
派浪人部队到宁海
Sending the ronins to Ninghai

925
01:09:54,700 --> 01:09:58,230
是要让戚继光的兵走一天的路去迎战
will make Qi's troops travel one day to fight.

926
01:09:58,790 --> 01:10:05,100
而我们在他迎击浪人的时候 进攻台州
We take Taizhou while they're engaged with the ronins.

927
01:10:05,580 --> 01:10:06,980
那新河呢
What about Xinhe?

928
01:10:07,450 --> 01:10:09,810
攻一个空的军营又是为什么
What's the point of attacking an empty barrack?

929
01:10:18,450 --> 01:10:23,480
戚继光和他军队的家人 都在新河呀
Qi and his troops' families are in Xinhe.

930
01:10:25,660 --> 01:10:28,390
保护战地
Between defending the land

931
01:10:29,660 --> 01:10:31,520
还是保护家人
and protecting their families,

932
01:10:33,910 --> 01:10:36,480
你说他们会选哪一个
how would they choose?

933
01:10:39,200 --> 01:10:42,560
无论他怎样选择
Whatever they choose to do,

934
01:10:43,290 --> 01:10:48,350
都会是个很有趣的局面
it'll be a very interesting situation.

935
01:10:50,870 --> 01:10:53,820
我们就在这里等他上钩
We'll wait for them to take the bait.

936
01:10:56,870 --> 01:11:00,430
过去倭寇来犯从来没有超过三千人
Pirates never brought more than 3,000 men.

937
01:11:01,040 --> 01:11:01,980
而这次
But this time,

938
01:11:02,910 --> 01:11:04,560
在奉化附近登岸的
20,000 pirates

939
01:11:04,660 --> 01:11:06,440
倭寇近有两万之众
landed near Fenghua.

940
01:11:08,080 --> 01:11:08,680
元敬
Jiguang,

941
01:11:09,000 --> 01:11:10,770
你的新兵只有三千
your new Army only has 3,000 men.

942
01:11:10,790 --> 01:11:12,190
怎么去迎战
How can you fight them?

943
01:11:13,200 --> 01:11:14,020
胡大人
Commander,

944
01:11:14,410 --> 01:11:17,230
你这是送羊入虎口
you are sending sheep to a tiger.

945
01:11:18,200 --> 01:11:18,930
卢大人
General Lu,

946
01:11:19,120 --> 01:11:20,400
我们可不是羊吶
we're not sheep.

947
01:11:20,700 --> 01:11:21,650
你别逞强
Don't get in over your head.

948
01:11:21,750 --> 01:11:23,940
那还要再等多长时间呀
How much longer must we wait?

949
01:11:26,000 --> 01:11:26,940
多等一天
The longer we wait,

950
01:11:27,080 --> 01:11:28,980
老百姓就要多受一天的苦
the longer our people will suffer.

951
01:11:29,700 --> 01:11:31,850
绝对不能让贼倭再深入下去了
We must stop the pirates' threat.

952
01:11:35,250 --> 01:11:36,470
其他同僚
Does anyone else

953
01:11:36,870 --> 01:11:39,570
真的没有一点对策了吗
have any counter measures?

954
01:11:51,500 --> 01:11:54,230
倭兵在宁海集结不动
Japanese soldiers congregated in Ninghai but made no moves

955
01:11:54,950 --> 01:11:57,230
就是要引你上钩呀
because they want you to take the bait.

956
01:11:57,790 --> 01:11:59,190
我愿意上这个钩
I'm willing to take the bait.

957
01:12:00,620 --> 01:12:03,070
如果我不上钩 对方就不会动
If I don't, they won't make a move.

958
01:12:04,200 --> 01:12:06,150
上次岑港之战我们知道
The battle of Cengang tells us

959
01:12:06,410 --> 01:12:08,560
对方有个懂兵法的人在调度
they have military strategists among them.

960
01:12:08,750 --> 01:12:11,020
这次很可能是同一批人
It's probably the same group.

961
01:12:12,540 --> 01:12:13,270
我建议
I suggest

962
01:12:13,620 --> 01:12:16,440
台州 象山的兵马按兵不动
troops in Taizhou and Xiangshan should lay low

963
01:12:16,700 --> 01:12:18,680
以防他们乘虚而入
to ensure the pirates can't take advantage of our weak defense.

964
01:12:19,290 --> 01:12:21,560
我愿意率领新军先打头阵
I'll take the lead with the new Army.

965
01:12:22,330 --> 01:12:24,180
等探明对方的意图之后
When we find out their real motive,

966
01:12:24,370 --> 01:12:25,940
再请大人定夺
we'll let Commander Hu make a ruling.

967
01:12:26,250 --> 01:12:27,140
这次
This time,

968
01:12:27,700 --> 01:12:29,560
绝对不能让他们再跑了
we won't let them get away again.

969
01:12:33,750 --> 01:12:34,440
好
Good!

970
01:12:36,120 --> 01:12:36,770
元敬
Jiguang,

971
01:12:38,370 --> 01:12:40,100
马上领军到宁海
set out for Ninghai right away.

972
01:12:40,910 --> 01:12:41,810
卢将军
General Lu,

973
01:12:42,450 --> 01:12:45,310
你呢 随我到台州坐镇
we'll take command of Taizhou.

974
01:12:45,700 --> 01:12:46,680
其余部队
The rest of the troops

975
01:12:47,290 --> 01:12:49,390
原地待命 加强防守
will stay put and beef up defense

976
01:12:49,790 --> 01:12:50,770
听候指令
pending our new order.

977
01:12:52,330 --> 01:12:53,520
大人英明
Good idea, Commander!

978
01:12:54,120 --> 01:12:56,100
大人英明
Good idea!

979
01:12:57,120 --> 01:12:59,940
不用你们打就是英明了 啊
Because you're not doing the fighting.

980
01:13:02,370 --> 01:13:03,570
就这么决定了
So be it.

981
01:13:10,580 --> 01:13:11,650
听说
I heard

982
01:13:12,950 --> 01:13:14,730
对方来了两万兵
the enemy has 20,000 men.

983
01:13:17,540 --> 01:13:18,360
别挂念
Don't worry!

984
01:13:19,410 --> 01:13:20,560
谢谢夫人
Thank you.

985
01:13:26,910 --> 01:13:28,060
两万
20,000 men.

986
01:13:28,580 --> 01:13:30,100
两万的倭寇
20,000 pirates.

987
01:13:30,620 --> 01:13:32,270
这仗能打得赢吗
Can we beat them?

988
01:13:32,450 --> 01:13:35,030
上次我们两万人打了一千倭寇
Last time we outnumbered them 20,000 to 1,000

989
01:13:35,450 --> 01:13:36,980
打了半年都没打完
and the war dragged on for 6 months.

990
01:13:37,660 --> 01:13:38,610
等等吧
Just wait.

991
01:13:42,410 --> 01:13:44,390
这帮人还不知道自己要去送死吗
Don't they know they're on a suicide mission?

992
01:13:45,120 --> 01:13:46,270
还威风呢
And they look so confident.

993
01:13:49,620 --> 01:13:50,600
说什么了
What did you say?

994
01:13:51,120 --> 01:13:52,270
有本事你去呀
I'd like to see you take their place.

995
01:13:53,660 --> 01:13:56,890
你们天天个个胆小鬼一样在这里耗着
You're a bunch of cowards hanging out here.

996
01:13:57,250 --> 01:13:58,270
有本事上战场
Why don't you go to the frontline?

997
01:13:58,330 --> 01:13:59,810
有什么权利说别人
You have no right to criticize.

998
01:14:02,580 --> 01:14:03,520
筷子
Chopsticks!

999
01:14:05,160 --> 01:14:06,610
胆小鬼
Cowards!

1000
01:14:09,000 --> 01:14:10,900
爹
Father!

1001
01:14:11,500 --> 01:14:12,900
慢点慢点
Slow down...

1002
01:14:41,540 --> 01:14:42,270
爹很快回来
We have to leave.

1003
01:14:59,250 --> 01:15:00,140
好走
Go...

1004
01:15:21,080 --> 01:15:22,060
头
Chief!

1005
01:15:22,410 --> 01:15:26,850
他们不会要我们去送死吧
Are they sending us on a suicide mission?

1006
01:15:27,120 --> 01:15:28,150
你这么怕死呀
Are you afraid to die?

1007
01:15:28,200 --> 01:15:29,480
怎么可能有这种事
How is this possible?

1008
01:15:29,910 --> 01:15:31,730
明军可以厉害到什么地步啊
How formidable is the Ming Army?

1009
01:15:34,370 --> 01:15:36,100
我们现在是最大的威胁
We're their biggest threat.

1010
01:15:37,450 --> 01:15:38,270
不过
But...

1011
01:15:38,830 --> 01:15:40,020
我担心的是
I'm more worried

1012
01:15:41,000 --> 01:15:42,940
他们一看见我们的身影
when they get a glimpse of us,

1013
01:15:43,540 --> 01:15:45,480
卷着尾巴就逃跑了
they'll run with their tails between their legs.

1014
01:15:49,580 --> 01:15:50,650
哎呀
Oh

1015
01:15:50,950 --> 01:15:53,100
我缺女人呀
I need women.

1016
01:15:53,500 --> 01:15:57,230
想起都觉得兴奋
The thought of them makes me excited.

1017
01:15:57,790 --> 01:16:00,110
明军快来
The Ming Army is coming!

1018
01:16:00,660 --> 01:16:03,770
快快打完我便去宁海找美女
Finish them off and I'll get a woman in Ninghai.

1019
01:16:03,790 --> 01:16:04,980
说的对
Absolutely!

1020
01:16:05,700 --> 01:16:08,360
傻瓜 女人和钱
If you want women and money,

1021
01:16:08,750 --> 01:16:10,230
当然都去台州
go to Taizhou.

1022
01:16:10,790 --> 01:16:13,440
台州才是大城
They have things that can satisfy us.

1023
01:16:14,000 --> 01:16:15,820
我缺钱呀
I need money.

1024
01:16:16,080 --> 01:16:19,860
打完这一仗赶紧向大人要报酬吧
Ask for our reward after this.

1025
01:16:20,330 --> 01:16:22,810
想回家了
I want to go home.

1026
01:16:23,750 --> 01:16:24,470
头
Chief!

1027
01:16:24,790 --> 01:16:26,310
明军就在前面了
The Ming Army is up ahead.

1028
01:16:27,620 --> 01:16:29,270
来送死的
