Aye!

1041
01:17:23,080 --> 01:17:23,810
听着
Listen up!

1042
01:17:24,540 --> 01:17:25,730
两边列阵
Split up the formation.

1043
01:17:44,040 --> 01:17:44,770
等等！
Wait!

1044
01:17:45,330 --> 01:17:46,060
准备枪
Rifles!

1045
01:17:46,700 --> 01:17:49,280
准备枪
Rifles!

1046
01:17:50,660 --> 01:17:51,640
开枪
Fire!

1047
01:18:03,910 --> 01:18:05,020
