Charge!

1048
01:18:33,910 --> 01:18:34,390
停呀
Stop!

1049
01:18:41,660 --> 01:18:42,480
挡
Block!

1050
01:18:56,870 --> 01:18:57,820
长枪
Spears!

1051
01:19:08,370 --> 01:19:08,850
拖走
Drag them away!

1052
01:19:10,120 --> 01:19:10,970
三眼铳
Three-eyed hand cannons!

1053
01:19:12,290 --> 01:19:12,940
蹲
Get down!

1054
