哥
Jiguang!

1060
01:19:38,660 --> 01:19:39,980
胡大人派兵来报
A message from Commander Hu.

1061
01:19:40,000 --> 01:19:41,480
新河附近发现倭兵
Japanese soldiers in Xinhe!

1062
01:19:44,000 --> 01:19:44,820
大成哥
Dacheng!

1063
01:19:45,540 --> 01:19:46,810
倭兵攻打我们家了
Japanese soldiers attacked our homes.

1064
01:19:49,000 --> 01:19:50,070
什么 你说什么
What did you say?

1065
01:19:50,250 --> 01:19:51,690
攻打我们家了 倭兵
Japanese soldiers attacked our homes.

1066
01:19:52,370 --> 01:19:53,400
大哥 怎么办
What should we do?

1067
01:19:55,620 --> 01:19:56,390
戚将军
General Qi,

1068
