可是嫂子在新河
your wife is there.

1091
01:20:42,120 --> 01:20:44,320
就是因为她在我才不担心
She's precisely the reason I'm not worried.

1092
01:20:45,370 --> 01:20:47,650
新河现在驻军就剩两百人
Only 200 men are stationed in Xinhe.

1093
01:20:48,040 --> 01:20:48,770
怎么行
That's not enough.

1094
01:20:49,750 --> 01:20:50,820
两百足够了
That's quite enough.

1095
01:20:52,040 --> 01:20:52,690
别忘了
Don't forget,

1096
01:20:52,830 --> 01:20:54,900
我夫人可是天下无敌啊
my wife is invincible.

1097
01:20:59,290 --> 01:21:00,060
要不这样
How about...

1098
01:21:00,370 --> 01:21:01,020
楼楠
Lou Nan!

1099
01:21:01,250 --> 01:21:04,230
你带领一半兵马先赶回去救援
Take half the troops with you back to Xinhe.

1100
01:21:04,370 --> 01:21:07,190
之后再赶回台州跟我们会合
Then meet us in Taizhou.

1101
01:21:07,790 --> 01:21:08,520
大成哥
Dacheng,

1102
01:21:08,700 --> 01:21:09,730
都说保家卫国
we should protect our homes and defend our state.

1103
01:21:10,080 --> 01:21:11,310
家都保不了 谈什么卫国
But without a home, who cares about the state?

1104
01:21:11,330 --> 01:21:11,900
闭嘴
Shut up!

1105
01:21:13,580 --> 01:21:14,810
戚将军都不担心
If General Qi is not worried,

1106
01:21:15,200 --> 01:21:16,270
你们担心什么呀
why should you be?

1107
01:21:16,830 --> 01:21:17,350
去
Go!

1108
01:21:17,870 --> 01:21:18,820
我们准备出发
Get ready to leave.

1109
01:21:18,950 --> 01:21:19,600
大成哥
Dacheng“.

1110
01:21:19,830 --> 01:21:20,520
去啊
Go!

1111
01:21:20,750 --> 01:21:21,600
走
Come on...

1112
01:21:27,250 --> 01:21:28,020
将军
General,

1113
01:21:29,040 --> 01:21:30,390
我军只有三千兵
we only have 3,000 men.

1114
01:21:31,120 --> 01:21:32,470
现在还一分为二
If we split the troops in half,

1115
01:21:33,040 --> 01:21:34,610
倭军人马两万呀
can we take on

1116
01:21:35,250 --> 01:21:36,100
可行吗
20,000 Japanese soldiers?

1117
01:21:36,410 --> 01:21:37,480
不行也得行
We'll have to.

1118
01:21:37,870 --> 01:21:39,020
台州不能失
We can't lose Taizhou.

1119
01:21:40,160 --> 01:21:42,770
大家的家眷可都托付给你了
Our families are in your good hands.

1120
01:21:43,410 --> 01:21:44,140
哥
Jiguang,

1121
01:21:45,160 --> 01:21:47,730
我们先去新河再去台州 也赶得及
we can still make Taizhou in time after Xinhe.

1122
01:21:48,410 --> 01:21:49,140
闭嘴
Shut up!

1123
01:21:50,000 --> 01:21:51,190
你再多说一个字
Another word out of you,

1124
01:21:51,370 --> 01:21:52,270
我先斩你
I'll have you beheaded.

1125
01:21:55,120 --> 01:21:55,690
好
Very well.

1126
01:21:55,910 --> 01:21:56,560
将军
General,

1127
01:21:57,500 --> 01:21:58,320
你放心
rest assured

1128
01:21:59,330 --> 01:22:00,900
如果新河有什么闪失
if anything happens to Xinhe,

1129
01:22:01,200 --> 01:22:02,060
我楼楠
Lou Nan

1130
01:22:02,370 --> 01:22:04,020
不会活着回来见你
will not come back alive.

1131
01:22:04,580 --> 01:22:05,350
拜托了
Thank you.

1132
01:22:12,620 --> 01:22:14,020
来 把东西全都装起来
Pack up everything.

1133
01:22:14,120 --> 01:22:15,900
能拿走的东西快拿走
Take whatever we can.

1134
01:22:16,370 --> 01:22:17,220
动作快点
On the double...

1135
01:22:22,830 --> 01:22:23,980
快 走
Go...

1136
01:22:28,330 --> 01:22:29,270
戚夫人
Madam Qi,

1137
01:22:29,790 --> 01:22:31,480
我怎么就跟你说不明白了
why can't you understand?

1138
01:22:31,500 --> 01:22:34,400
这上万的倭兵马上要到新河城了
Over 10,000 Japanese soldiers will be in Xinhe soon.

1139
01:22:34,500 --> 01:22:37,770
我们已经派人去找戚将军去了
I already sent a message to General Qi.

1140
01:22:38,160 --> 01:22:40,730
你现在听我的赶紧收拾精致细软
Listen to me and pack your things.

1141
01:22:41,250 --> 01:22:42,600
卑职送你出城
I'll escort you out of town.

1142
01:22:42,620 --> 01:22:44,270
我们出城那新河怎么办
Then what will happen to Xinhe?

1143
01:22:46,830 --> 01:22:48,560
黄岩的乡兵
Village soldiers are

1144
01:22:48,580 --> 01:22:51,400
和太平的乡兵现在就在城外抵抗
fighting outside the city right now.

1145
01:22:51,830 --> 01:22:53,520
这整个县衙之内
We have less than

1146
01:22:53,540 --> 01:22:56,770
新河城之内就不到两百个衙役呀
200 soldiers in Xinhe,

1147
01:22:56,830 --> 01:22:57,930
- 能顶得…  - 戚夫人
- how can... - Madam Qi!

1148
01:22:58,250 --> 01:22:59,470
他们说倭寇来了
They say the pirates are coming.

1149
01:22:59,500 --> 01:23:00,220
我们该怎么办
What should we do?

1150
01:23:00,290 --> 01:23:01,230
你看你看
See?

1151
01:23:06,410 --> 01:23:08,640
马上找人敲钟 召集全城老百姓
Sound the bell and summon everyone in town.

1152
01:23:10,040 --> 01:23:10,690
走 赶紧
Let's go!

1153
01:23:10,700 --> 01:23:12,310
小牟去把盔甲拿来
Xiao Mou, bring my armor.

1154
01:23:12,580 --> 01:23:13,980
你们要干什么
What are you doing?

1155
01:23:14,870 --> 01:23:15,970
走走走赶紧
Hurry up...

1156
01:23:16,330 --> 01:23:17,400
这以为做假装的
You think this is a game?

1157
01:23:18,000 --> 01:23:19,770
这是打仗要死人吶
We're going to war. People may die.

1158
01:23:19,870 --> 01:23:21,690
倭寇你见过嘛 我见过
Have you seen a pirate? I have.

1159
01:23:22,040 --> 01:23:23,560
我杀过
I killed some of them.

1160
01:23:25,910 --> 01:23:27,060
再不走就来不及了
Time is running out.

1161
01:23:39,290 --> 01:23:41,790
我是戚将军夫人
I am General Qi's wife.

1162
01:23:41,790 --> 01:23:44,770
我没有办法扔下新河的老百姓自己逃命
I cannot run away and abandon the people of Xinhe.

1163
01:23:45,040 --> 01:23:46,190
你若想走
If you want to leave,

1164
01:23:46,950 --> 01:23:47,930
请自便
go ahead.

1165
01:23:51,700 --> 01:23:53,900
我怎么就跟她说不明白了
Why can't I reason with her?

1166
01:23:58,330 --> 01:23:59,930
走走走
Let's go.

1167
01:24:03,790 --> 01:24:04,390
别走别走
Don't go!

1168
01:24:06,250 --> 01:24:07,140
跑了也没有用
What's the use of running?

1169
01:24:07,500 --> 01:24:08,520
还不如跟他们拼了吶
Might as well stay and fight.

1170
01:24:12,040 --> 01:24:12,770
来来来
Come on...

1171
01:24:13,200 --> 01:24:14,650
戚夫人带人来拿兵器了
Madam Qi came to get weapons.

1172
01:24:15,290 --> 01:24:17,440
不是说好了那有人把守的吗
Didn't we agree someone will guard the city?

1173
01:24:17,500 --> 01:24:18,570
都给打晕了
They were knocked out cold.

1174
01:24:24,410 --> 01:24:25,230
夫人 你等一下
Wait up, Madam!

1175
01:24:25,330 --> 01:24:26,100
让开
Step aside!

1176
01:24:26,790 --> 01:24:28,110
让开
Step aside!

1177
01:24:28,200 --> 01:24:29,520
你们别走了
Don%leave!

1178
01:24:47,910 --> 01:24:48,610
你们别走呀
Don%leave!

1179
01:24:49,080 --> 01:24:50,930
大娘来 喝喝水吧
Auntie, drink some water.

1180
01:24:51,540 --> 01:24:52,640
当心自己
Be careful!

1181
01:24:53,660 --> 01:24:54,860
大爷喝喝水
Here, drink some water.

1182
01:24:58,370 --> 01:24:58,940
夫人
Madam,

1183
01:24:59,080 --> 01:25:01,730
戚将军 能赶回来吗
will General Qi be back in time?

1184
01:25:03,200 --> 01:25:04,150
他会回来的
Yes, he will.

1185
01:25:05,000 --> 01:25:05,940
那就好
That's good.

1186
01:25:06,200 --> 01:25:07,310
大家都放心吧
Don't worry, folks.

1187
01:25:07,620 --> 01:25:08,900
戚将军一定会赶回来的
General Qi will be back.

1188
01:25:09,620 --> 01:25:10,850
好好好
Very well.

1189
01:25:10,870 --> 01:25:12,690
我们拼了老命也守住
We'll guard the city with our lives.

1190
01:25:14,200 --> 01:25:14,980
杨大哥
Brother Yang,

1191
01:25:20,160 --> 01:25:21,310
你们怎么回来了
what are you doing here?

1192
01:25:22,250 --> 01:25:23,320
你们不怕死吗
You're not afraid to die?

1193
01:25:27,250 --> 01:25:28,190
怕死
Am.

1194
01:25:28,870 --> 01:25:30,270
只是夫人不走
But if you're staying,

1195
01:25:30,870 --> 01:25:32,350
我们又怎么能走呢
how can we leave

1196
01:25:33,290 --> 01:25:34,890
让后辈子孙笑呀
and become the laughing stock?

1197
01:25:38,200 --> 01:25:38,560
你
You...

1198
01:25:38,580 --> 01:25:39,430
大哥
Brother...

1199
01:25:39,660 --> 01:25:41,360
去教他们三眼铳
Teach them how to use the hand cannons.

1200
01:25:41,370 --> 01:25:42,350
来兄弟们
Come on...

1201
01:25:43,080 --> 01:25:43,770
夫人
Madam,

1202
01:25:44,250 --> 01:25:47,100
守城 是我的责任
it's my duty to guard the city.

1203
01:25:47,910 --> 01:25:49,020
交给我吧
Leave that to me.

1204
01:25:53,910 --> 01:25:54,640
后面跟上
Keep UP...

1205
01:25:54,910 --> 01:25:55,440
快
Hurry!

1206
01:25:55,910 --> 01:25:57,480
将士们坚持
Keep it UP...

1207
01:26:00,660 --> 01:26:03,140
我们一定要坚持 快
We shall prevail! Hurry!

1208
01:26:07,830 --> 01:26:10,560
我们深夜才行动
Wait till midnight to make our move.

1209
01:26:10,700 --> 01:26:11,520
是
Aye!

1210
01:26:11,910 --> 01:26:12,980
跑 都给我加快
Run! Hurry up!

1211
01:26:13,870 --> 01:26:14,640
跑
Run!

1212
01:26:22,950 --> 01:26:25,430
头他们更起劲了
Chief, they seem quite energetic.

1213
01:26:26,040 --> 01:26:28,310
就让戚继光多活几个时辰吧
Let Qi live a few more hours.

1214
01:26:29,790 --> 01:26:31,730
自己部队中计都不知
He doesn't know he's walking into a trap.

1215
01:26:33,040 --> 01:26:35,350
戚继光和老狐狸互打的时候
When he takes on the sly old fox,

1216
01:26:35,370 --> 01:26:37,100
