we'll ambush them from behind.

1217
01:26:39,080 --> 01:26:40,180
妙计
Brilliant!

1218
01:26:41,200 --> 01:26:42,060
报告戚将军
General,

1219
01:26:42,330 --> 01:26:44,730
一股倭兵在城府四里外花街镇札营
the Japanese soldiers encamped in Huajie, 4 miles outside the city.

1220
01:26:44,910 --> 01:26:47,640
城府中 胡大人和三千官兵已做好布防
Commander Hu and 3,000 men have already set up defense in the city.

1221
01:26:49,120 --> 01:26:50,350
果然是台州
They're after Taizhou after all.

1222
01:26:51,750 --> 01:26:53,070
敌军人数是多少
How many men do they have?

1223
01:26:53,370 --> 01:26:54,940
他们大概有八千到一万左右
Between 8,000 to 10,000.

1224
01:26:57,000 --> 01:26:58,320
继美 军旗
Jimei! Banner!

1225
01:26:58,370 --> 01:26:58,810
是
Aye!

1226
01:27:00,330 --> 01:27:00,900
哥
Here!

1227
01:27:03,200 --> 01:27:06,060
把我的军旗交给台州城府的胡大人
Give this to Commander Hu.

1228
01:27:06,500 --> 01:27:07,520
请他们挂起来
Ask him to hoist it.

1229
01:27:07,620 --> 01:27:09,400
就说我马上回来取
Tell him I'll be back for it.

1230
01:27:09,750 --> 01:27:10,600
遵命
Aye!

1231
01:27:11,830 --> 01:27:12,560
走
Let's go!

1232
01:27:22,450 --> 01:27:25,310
宁海的浪人部队已经被他打败
If ronins defeated him in Ninghai.

1233
01:27:25,790 --> 01:27:29,850
那我便让浪人去进攻台州
I'll let the ronins attack Taizhou

1234
01:27:31,580 --> 01:27:34,100
我们的部队依然发毫不损
and our troops won't suffer any casualties.

1235
01:27:34,620 --> 01:27:38,900
这太让人气馁了
That is so discouraging.

1236
01:27:43,700 --> 01:27:46,060
只要除掉戚继光
